These 3d print files are for a steady, which fits onto the AliExpress 9cm x 9cm lifting table

The files were orginally made to fit the table I ordred, being 88mm x88mm.

21/04/2026 It was reported (thanks for the feedback) that a user's table, ordered from AliExpress, was 90mm x 90mm
thus the print file was slightly too small.

The file has been modified to fit a 90mm table.

If you have the smaller table (like me) there will be a little more play left/right
which is not an issue once the print is secured to the table top.
